                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>you will please acknowledge receipt<lb/> of enclosed draft by return of mail<lb/> and\n                oblige yours truly</p>\n            <p><persName role=\"author\">J. Dyer</persName>.</p>\n            <p>Statement</p>\n            <table cols=\"2\" rows=\"6\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Paid <persName>W. S. Jutt<add>?</add></persName> Rev. Tax on Legacy\n                        $2000</cell>\n                    <cell>120</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Balance due you “ “</cell>\n                    <cell>1880</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Subscription for 4 Copies of Occident</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">16</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$ 2016</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Less U S Rev Tax</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">120</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>To Draft enclosed for</cell>\n                    <cell>$18.96</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
